<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_87e447468c9e.aspx"><b>静女</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson87e447468c9e">
静女其姝，俟我于城隅。爱而不见，搔首踟蹰。<br />静女其娈，贻我彤管。彤管有炜，说怿女美。<br />自牧归荑，洵美且异。匪女之为美，美人之贻。
</div>
